{"tid":1287013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再理武漢單野！咪再理武漢單野！","createTime":"2019-07-05T04:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T06:18:27.000Z","uid":264683,"like":75,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f0bb7b1a936504acde03279dd8563dca87d144fe","tid":1287013,"uid":264683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"我係p牌 但係見倒咁多人撐聲援武漢單野真係忍唔住出聲<br />\n首先武漢係反垃圾場，唔係反共呀<br />\n佢地唔會想同香港扯上任何政治關係<br />\n<br />\n喺大陸，香港示威者係被扣上港獨帽子<br />\n我地聲援，只會比更多政治彈藥中共<br />\n最壞情況：到時共狗有藉口將事件政治化，將武漢示威同國家安全扯上關係<br />\n佢地會面臨咩後果？<br />\n我地最唔想面對嘅送中審判，顛覆政權又好，反革命罪又好，到時垃圾場照起，中共又解決晒提出問題嘅人<br />\n<br />\n咁對我地有咩影響？<br />\n無論武漢接唔接受我地聲援<br />\n係我地聲援個刻<br />\n輿論上我地就正式成為國家級叛亂份子<br />\n中共一定會落我地數<br />\n政苦更大條道理重啟送中，23條<br />\n到時真係不得了<br />\n<br />\n小結：咁做根本只會損害兩邊示威陣型<br />\n<br />\n咁我地可以做乜？<br />\n就係由佢地自己亂<br />\n我地自己香港自己救<br />\n佢地自己家園唔可以自己救<br />\n佢地有本事大可以學我地爭取國際支持<br />\n<br />\n我地戰線應該集中香港，唔好比人分化<br />\n死左四個人喇，我地更加輸唔起！"},{"pid":"d9b0e4f480b2c86738be0ad6612f944780dafb15","tid":1287013,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:51:13.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe7c5235291ae7d856e01fddd23a71cbe3d315dd","tid":1287013,"uid":75790,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:53:48.000Z","msg":"係35毛扮香港人理喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地邊有咁得閒"},{"pid":"b12496e16f2beaf111ad6e7bef8297be5bbae4a1","tid":1287013,"uid":88628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZsEsW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZsEsW.gif&h=c3ba57e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38bd22ec70c007c31ea0974ee9fd8ff105a921e8","tid":1287013,"uid":270179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"唔好俾人分化到<br />\n冇人話要反攻大陸<br />\n只係要燒佢後欄<br />\n不割席<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不沉船<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n1.撤回條例<br />\n2.釋放義士<br />\n3.取消暴動定性<br />\n4.追究警方濫用武力鎮壓<br />\n5.落實雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HtoEwdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtoEwdk.png&h=45ccf763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Np0Z6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Np0Z6F.png&h=d451cb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/05/145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2F145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png&h=2adf7012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a736414054083e98c39b14d8fb50370fa2e246cf","tid":1287013,"uid":47298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:59:43.000Z","msg":"講可以繼續講呀<br />\n網上和理非好啱做呢啲"},{"pid":"a00535eda5f2a97a44c57f4fe06d205f4459a2c3","tid":1287013,"uid":47298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a736414054083e98c39b14d8fb50370fa2e246cf","tid":1287013,"uid":47298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:59:43.000Z","msg":"講可以繼續講呀<br />\n網上和理非好啱做呢啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:00:18.000Z","msg":"前提係我哋唔係聲援<br />\n而係要人知武漢嘅事"},{"pid":"1bd3be3f94a9ffd0b552e83ed944d70c55a74af7","tid":1287013,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:00:20.0